title: Unable to log into account
description: Customer is having trouble logging into their account after recent password change.

title: Refund not processed
description: Customer has requested a refund for an order but has not received any update.

title: Missing order items
description: Customer received their order but one item is missing from the package.

title: Shipping delay
description: Customer’s order has not been shipped on the promised date. Needs update.

title: Broken product received
description: Customer received a damaged item and wants a replacement.

title: Account security concern
description: Customer reports unauthorized access to their account.

title: Subscription cancellation
description: Customer wants to cancel their subscription but is facing issues with the process.

title: Change of shipping address
description: Customer needs to update their shipping address before the order is dispatched.

title: Discount code not working
description: Customer is unable to apply a discount code during checkout.

title: Order status not updated
description: Customer’s order status still shows as 'processing' even though it was shipped.

title: Unable to track order
description: Customer cannot track their order using the provided tracking number.

title: Product not as described
description: Customer received the wrong product, and it does not match the description on the website.
